      </li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n              <strong class=\"w-6 text-editorial-gold\">•</strong>\n              <span class=\"muted\">Automation — tests, linters and CI snippets that integrate with your pipeline.</span>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n              <strong class=\"w-6 text-editorial-gold\">•</strong>\n              <span class=\"muted\">Iterative fixes — propose minimal diffs and explain changes in plain language.</span>\n            </li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"lg:col-span-6\">\n          <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n            <figure class=\"hero-clip overflow-hidden rounded-lg fade-up delay-2 hover-pop\" style=\"animation-fill-mode:both;\">\n              <img class=\"img-cover\" src=\"https://picsum.photos/seed/feature1/600/400\" alt=\"Pair programming session showing two developers discussing a terminal output\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n            </figure>\n\n            <figure class=\"hero-clip overflow-hidden rounded-lg fade-up delay-3 hover-pop\" style=\"animation-fill-mode:both;\">\n              <img class=\"img-cover\" src=\"https://picsum.photos/seed/feature2/600/400\" alt=\"Design canvas with a component library and responsive previews\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n            </figure>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- Features / Capabilities -->\n    <section id=\"features\" class=\"mb-16\">\n      <h3 class=\"sr-only\">Capabilities</h3>\n      <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\">\n        <article class=\"bg-white rounded-lg p-5 hero-clip hover-pop fade-up delay-1 focus-ring\" style=\"animation-fill-mode:both;\">\n          <img class=\"img-cover h-40 w-full rounded-md mb-4\" src=\"https://picsum.photos/seed/feature3/600/400\" alt=\"Automated tests running in a terminal with passing results\" loading=\"lazy\"/>\n          <h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold\" style=\"font-family:'Playfair Display', serif;\">Code & Tests</h4>\n          <p class=\"muted mt-2 text-sm\">Generate small, reviewable code changes with unit and integration tests. Output is geared for CI pipelines and code review.</p>\n        </article>\n\n        <article class=\"bg-white rounded-lg p-5 hero-clip hover-pop fade-up delay-2 focus-ring\" style=\"animation-fill-mode:both;\">\n          <img class=\"img-cover h-40 w-full rounded-md mb-4\" src=\"https://picsum.photos/seed/coffee2/600/400\" alt=\"A responsive UI component displayed across device screens\" loading=\"lazy\"/>\n          <h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold\" style=\"font-family:'Playfair Display', serif;\">Design to Component</h4>\n          <p class=\"muted mt-2 text-sm\">Translate Figma or PNG designs into responsive, accessible HTML/CSS or componentized React code with a consistent design system.</p>\n        </article>\n\n        <article class=\"bg-white rounded-lg p-5 hero-clip hover-pop fade-up delay-3 focus-ring\" style=\"animation-fill-mode:both;\">\n          <img class=\"img-cover h-40 w-full rounded-md mb-4\" src=\"https://picsum.photos/seed/coffee3/600/400\" alt=\"A CI pipeline dashboard showing build and deployment stages\" loading=\"lazy\"/>\n          <h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold\" style=\"font-family:'Playfair Display', serif;\">CI & Delivery</h4>\n          <p class=\"muted mt-2 text-sm\">Create CI scripts, deployment steps, and automated checks so changes are verified before merge — clear guidance and ready-to-run snippets.</p>\n        </article>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- CTA / Contact -->\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"mb-20\">\n      <div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg p-6 sm:p-8 hero-clip flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 fade-up delay-1\" style=\"animation-fill-mode:both;\">\n        <div>\n          <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold\" style=\"font-family:'Playfair Display', serif;\">Ready to try a repository